{
  "stem": "8775.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] And as far as friends, my friends consisted mainly of the pals I had in the elementary school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "As I mentioned, it was a Jewish elementary school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And there were four classes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In other words, from first to four grade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And my friends mainly consisted of the boys and the girls who were my classmates.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I was a very studious person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I was always on the top of the list.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I had to be, because as I said, my father was the head of the school board and he expected it of me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And for reward, after the finals were passed, or the certificates were given out, for rewards we went to a pastry shop, where me and some other kids were given ice cream and pies.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And this was from the first year, which was in 1937, to 1940.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "These were the years, which were pretty happy years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I remember them with great pride.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I'm very happy about those years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were many Jewish families in the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, there was also a young girl who went to my class.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were other people as well, Christian people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but I didn't know the children that well in the street, except the ones I, I went to the elementary school with.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, during the high holy days, we had a-- we had a ball actually, because in the temple's garden, we were playing around.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sometimes the old members of the temple came out and shushed us, you know that we should-- that we are making too much noise and we are distracting them from their prayers.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these were the times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I didn't have too many non-Jewish friends in those years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
